messages.message: I have been pushing out a lot of messaging this week for people to create an AI Hub account, is it possible to see a list of new users that are created to see if it is one of my leads, so I can follow up?

Hey - We do have a list of all the registered users. This will be made available to @Conor and team via automated data dump. Given this is sensitive user information, we want to be careful in giving access. Can you work with Conor and team on this? Thanks
